milestones.description: Porterfield has become the top scorer for IRE in ODIs with 391 runs, going past Kevin O'Brien's 320
Bas Zuiderent and Reekers's 114-run partnership is NED's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 67 between Bas Zuiderent and Eric
Eoin Morgan and Porterfield's 153-run partnership is IRE's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 78 between Andre Botha and Porterfield
Reekers has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (66) in an innings in ODIs for NED, going past Klaas-Jan van Noortwijk's 62
Tim de Leede has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (26) for NED, going past Bas Zuiderent
Andre Botha has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (8) for IRE, going past Johnston
This is the highest match aggregate (514) involving teams Netherlands & Ireland in ODIs
Netherlands's 7-run win against Ireland is the smallest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 17-run win against Canada
